    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a collector-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart lies the S54B32 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system for razor-sharp throttle response. This example features a precise 6-speed manual transmission paired with a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal power delivery. The chassis integrity is absolute, with a factory-perfect subframe and zero oxidation. Every bushing, link, and damper remains in peak operational condition, preserving the original suspension geometry and feedback. This is a mechanically flawless specimen for the discerning purist.",
